---
title: Easy Keema-Style Lamb Curry & Rice with Steamed Baby Broccoli
description: Heat up your nights with aromatic spices, perfect for any lamb dish and top-tier in a keema-style curry. The rice will help to soak it up so you don’t miss out on a single drop of this decadent curry.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
